full_text: When Ghisiane Maxwell first arrived in the unit, She introduced herself to everyone with a handshake."Hi l'am Maxwell" She says with a smile genuine and kind. It took all of us by surprise. Within one week of Maxwell arriving, She had volunteered to teach ESL, Teach Yoga, and help women with their GED. I believe It's important to know that there are also positive opinions, some of which are among inmates in the Unit. I believe that is also good to point out the good in people. ~Tatiana Venegas
